text: One North Wacker, formerly UBS Tower is a 50-story, skyscraper at One North Wacker Drive in Chicago, Illinois. Construction began in 1999 and was completed in the spring of 2002. ==References== ==Other websites== *One North Wacker at Hines Interests Limited Partnership *One North Wacker Architecture at Enclos Category:Skyscrapers in Chicago Category:2002 establishments in the United States Category:2000s establishments in Illinois
